WESTERN SOUTH ATLANTIC.
URUGUAY.
1. SEISMIC SURVEY 14 OCT BY M/V RAMFORM VANGUARD TOWING
   12 7000 METER LONG CABLES ALONG TRACKLINES BETWEEN:
   A. 35-19.33S 052-40.73W AND 35-08.07S 052-29.53W.
   B. 35-08.53S 052-32.53W AND 35-19.52S 053-43.48W.
   C. 35-29.87S 052-54.87W AND 35-40.83S 053-05.92W.
   NINE MILE BERTH REQUESTED.
2. CANCEL THIS MSG 15 OCT 13.
